CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FThe NHS has launched a public
OL,7,Fconsultation on plans to move a small
OL,8,Fnumber of Liverpool's high-risk births
OL,9,Fand complex gynaecology operations
OL,10,Ffrom Liverpool Women's Hospital to
OL,11,FRoyal Liverpool Hospital.
OL,13,FThe proposal, by the NHS Cheshire and
OL,14,FMerseyside, aims to improve safety for
OL,15,Fwomen requiring highly specialised
OL,16,Fcare by bringing services closer to
OL,17,Fadult critical care, emergency
OL,18,Ftreatment and specialised surgical
OL,19,Fteams.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FWithin the plans, approximately 1% of
OL,7,Fall maternity and gynaecology cases,
OL,8,Fwould be affected.
OL,10,FCurrently, most of these births and
OL,11,Foperations take place at Liverpool
OL,12,FWomen's Hospital, a mile away, but the
OL,13,FNHS said this can cause "significant
OL,14,Fproblems in providing safe and timely
OL,15,Fcare to women", especially for the
OL,16,Fmost seriously ill patients.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FWhile it is not always possible to
OL,7,Fpredict who will need specialist or
OL,8,Fcritical care services, health service
OL,9,Fsays it will make care safer for women
OL,10,Fundergoing planned complex and high-
OL,11,Frisk procedures, such as pelvic
OL,12,Fsurgery.
OL,14,FDr Fiona Lemmens, Executive Clinical
OL,15,FDirector for NHS Cheshire and
OL,16,FMerseyside said: "We know that it
OL,17,Fwon't solve every problem related to
OL,18,Fhaving gynaecology and maternity
OL,19,Fservices on a separate site from other
OL,20,Fspecialist adult services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,F"However, it will make a big
OL,7,Fdifference to some of our most
OL,8,Fseriously unwell patients, and we
OL,9,Fthink it's the right thing to do what
OL,10,Fwe can to improve care now, as well as
OL,11,Fcontinuing to work on longer-term
OL,12,Fsolutions."
OL,14,FThe changes would support
OL,15,Fapproximately 30 pregnant women per
OL,16,Fyear who have serious medical
OL,17,Fconditions that need managing
OL,18,Falongside their delivery, such as
OL,19,Fcongenital heart disease and kidney
OL,20,Fdisease requiring dialysis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FWomen who are likely to need intensive
OL,7,Fcare support when they have their baby
OL,8,Fwill also benefit from the move to
OL,9,FRoyal Liverpool Hospital, the NHS say.
OL,11,FCheshire and Merseyside NHS said: "In
OL,12,Feach instance, the clinical team
OL,13,Fcaring for these women would have
OL,14,Fdetailed discussions with them about
OL,15,Ftheir care options, ahead of putting
OL,16,Fthis arrangement in place."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FThe proposal includes a new dedicated
OL,7,Fspace within Royal Liverpool Hospital
OL,8,Ffor gynaecology operations and high-
OL,9,Frisk births and neonatal support, as
OL,10,Fwell as an enhanced care unit and more
OL,11,Fspecialist support at Liverpool
OL,12,FWomen's.
OL,14,FThis would cost around #5.5 million to
OL,15,Fcreate, and a further #2.2 million
OL,16,Feach year to staff and resource.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FThe NHS say the support would also
OL,7,Fexpand beyond those two hospitals with
OL,8,Fan enhanced midwifery outreach
OL,9,Fservice, and some outpatient
OL,10,Fgynaecology and maternity clinics at
OL,11,FAintree Hospital to improve access for
OL,12,Fwomen from north Liverpool who might
OL,13,Ffind it harder to travel into
OL,14,FLiverpool city centre for appointments.
OL,16,FThere will be a six-week public
OL,17,Fengagement from 2 June to 14 July 2026
OL,18,Fto consult on the issue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
