PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780416668
OL,3,CNHS proposes moving high-risk birth
OL,4,Ccare from Liverpool Women's Hospital
OL,6,FThere will also be three public
OL,7,Finformation events taking place, which
OL,8,Fwill be an opportunity for people to
OL,9,Fhear more about the plans, and ask any
OL,10,Fquestions they might have:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
